 <h1 class="section-heading text-highlight">
	<span class="line">Message From Chairman</span>
	</h1>
    <div class="section-content">                     
     <div class="entry-content">
       <p style="text-align: justify;">I have become highly pleased to be informed that Barisal Model School &amp; College has successfully introduced its inter active wed service for its teachers, staffs, guardians, students as well as for all. I think this service will intensify the eagerness of the students to be acquainted with the mission of digitalizing Bangladesh. I am highly satisfied with the principal of this institution because his tireless activities have paved the way to implement such kind of brilliant job. Its needed to acknowledge that digital institution ensure an ICT driven knowledge-based society where information will be readily available on line and where all possible tasks of the government, semi-government and also private spheres will be processed using the modern technology.</p>
       <p style="text-align: justify;">It is evident that this its inter active wed service will be a role model for all the institutions across the country as gradually it will become an eventful phenomenon for all the guardians to be conscious about the performance and academic activities of their children. I believe Bangladesh being resounding with the target of achieving of digital Bangladesh being powered by this service. Due to globalization, Bangladesh has already been connected with the outside world and for this, our institution can not be exception to that building strong ICT infrastructure is the pre-requisite for making any institution digital one. I perceive this inter active wed service will bring an abrupt change in academic progress and will uplift the institution to a supreme position in the country, In fine l like to thank the principal for his outstanding effort, and his colleagues who are involved in implementing this inter active wed service.</p>
       <p style="text-align: justify;">I wish all students, best future and believe that they will renew their hopes for greater responsibilities with the target of building of ICT based, corruption free developed Bangladesh.</p>
       <p style="text-align: justify;">May Allah- The Almighty bestow His divine mercy and blessing to all of us.</p>
       <p style="text-align: justify;">Divisional Commissioner<br>
       President<br>
       Board of Governors<br>
       Barisal Model School &amp; College<br>
       Barisal</p>
